<mjml>
  <!-- Attributes -->
  <mj-head>
    <mj-attributes>
      <mj-all font-family="Barlow" />
      <mj-class
        name="text10"
        color="#FFFFFF"
        font-weight="500"
        font-size="10px"
        line-height="20px"
        padding-top="0"
        padding-bottom="16px"
      />
      <mj-class
        name="mainText"
        color="#27354E"
        font-weight="600"
        font-size="12px"
        line-height="20px"
        letter-spacing="1%"
      />
      <mj-class
        name="footnoteText"
        color="#7F8A9D"
        font-weight="300"
        font-size="10px"
        line-height="20px"
        letter-spacing="1%"
        align="center"
      />
    </mj-attributes>
  </mj-head>

  <mj-body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <mj-section background-color="#304872" padding="10px 20px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image
          src="https://isunfa.tw/email/isunfa_logo.png?w=32&q=75"
          alt="isunfa_logo"
          width="80px"
          align="left"
        ></mj-image>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Main -->
    <mj-section background-color="#F4F5F7" padding="40px">
      <mj-column background-color="#FFFFFF" padding="20px 40px">
        <mj-text font-size="18px" line-height="28px" font-weight="600" color="#FFA502"
          >陽光智能會計已調整為免費版</mj-text
        >

        <mj-text mj-class="mainText">
          親愛的
          <span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; color: #cc8401">{{receiverName}}</span>
          您好,
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text mj-class="mainText">
          由於近期付款未成功，我們已暫時將您的帳戶權限調整為免費版方案。 <br />
          目前您將無法使用部分進階功能，但所有資料均已妥善保留， <br />
          無需擔心遺失或損毀。
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text mj-class="mainText"
          >目前方案：
          <span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; color: #cc8401">{{currentPlanName}}</span
          ><br />
          帳戶資料狀態：<span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; color: #2d7e58"
            >{{currentDataStatus}}</span
          ><br />
          恢復訂閱：您可隨時升級回原專業版或企業版，恢復所有功能與使用權限，
          過程不會影響任何歷史資料。</mj-text
        >
        <mj-text mj-class="mainText">
          若您希望繼續使用完整功能，請登入系統更新付款方式或重新啟用訂閱：
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text align="left">
          <a
            href="{{repayLink}}"
            style="
              display: inline-block;
              border: 1px solid #ffa502;
              background-color: white;
              color: #cc8401;
              padding: 8px 16px;
              text-decoration: none;
              border-radius: 5px;
              font-size: 14px;
              line-height: 20px;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-right: 16px;
            "
          >
            更新付款
          </a>

          <a
            href="{{resubscribeLink}}"
            style="
              display: inline-block;
              border: 1px solid #ffa502;
              background-color: white;
              color: #cc8401;
              padding: 8px 16px;
              text-decoration: none;
              border-radius: 5px;
              font-size: 14px;
              line-height: 20px;
              font-weight: 500;
            "
          >
            重新訂閱
          </a>
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text mj-class="mainText"
          >我們了解每一位創業者對數據的重視，因此無論您目前是否維持付費狀態，
          我們都致力保障您的資料完整與安全。如有任何問題，也歡迎您隨時與我們聯繫，我們期待在未來繼續為您提供協助。
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text mj-class="mainText"
          >敬祝<br />一切順利、事業發展順心 <br />陽光智能會計團隊 敬上</mj-text
        >

        <mj-text mj-class="footnoteText"> ※此封郵件為系統信件，請勿直接回覆 </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <mj-section background-color="#304872" padding="40px">
      <!-- 左邊區塊 -->
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text color="#FFFFFF" font-weight="700" font-size="12px" line-height="28px" padding="0"
          >Contact Us</mj-text
        >
        <mj-text
          mj-class="text10"
          padding="0"
          padding-bottom="8px"
          align="left"
          vertical-align="middle"
        >
          <img width="10px" src="https://isunfa.tw/email/mail_inbox.png?w=32&q=75" />
          <a
            href="mailto:isunfahelp@isunfa.com.tw"
            style="color: white; font-weight: 500; font-size: 10px; text-decoration: none"
            >isunfahelp@isunfa.com.tw</a
          ></mj-text
        >
        <mj-text
          mj-class="text10"
          padding="0"
          padding-bottom="8px"
          align="left"
          vertical-align="middle"
        >
          <img width="10px" src="https://isunfa.tw/email/phone_ringing.png?w=32&q=75" />
          <a
            href="tel:+886-2-2700-1979"
            style="color: white; font-weight: 500; font-size: 10px; text-decoration: none"
            >+886-2-2700-1979</a
          ></mj-text
        >
        <mj-text
          mj-class="text10"
          padding="0"
          padding-bottom="8px"
          align="left"
          vertical-align="middle"
        >
          <span
            ><img width="10px" src="https://isunfa.tw/email/alarm_clock.png?w=32&q=75" /> Service
            Hours :
          </span>
          <br />
          <span style="margin-left: 12px"> Mon to Fri, 09:00 AM - 06:00 PM.</span>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>

      <!-- 右邊區塊：icon + text -->
      <mj-column padding-top="50px">
        <mj-text align="right" padding="0">
          <mj-text style="margin-right: 24px">
            <a href="https://isunfa.tw/" target="_blank"
              ><img
                src="https://isunfa.tw/email/isunfa_logo.png?w=32&q=75"
                alt="isunfa_logo"
                width="80px"
            /></a>
          </mj-text>
          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61555435381112" target="_blank">
            <img
              width="20px"
              src="https://img.icons8.com/m_rounded/512/FFFFFF/facebook-new.png"
              alt="facebook_link"
              style="margin-right: 12px"
            />
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/CAFECA-IO/iSunFA" target="_blank">
            <img
              width="20px"
              src="https://img.icons8.com/ios11/512/FFFFFF/github.png"
              alt="github_link"
              style="margin-right: 12px"
          /></a>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@isunfa" target="_blank"
            ><img
              width="20px"
              src="https://img.icons8.com/ios11/512/FFFFFF/youtube-play.png"
              alt="youtube_link"
          /></a>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text
          color="#FFFFFF"
          font-size="10px"
          padding="0"
          font-weight="400"
          align="right"
          padding-top="16px"
          >iSunFA @ 2024. All rights reserved.</mj-text
        >
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
